# Normalize line endings to LF for all text files in the repo.
# Reason: Repo is checked out on Windows (dev) and Linux (Hetzner deploy).
# Without this, Windows editors silently rewrite files as CRLF and
# pollute every diff. With eol=lf, Git stores LF in the index AND
# writes LF to the working tree on every platform.

* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary files -- never touch these
*.png   binary
*.jpg   binary
*.jpeg  binary
*.gif   binary
*.pdf   binary
*.zip   binary
*.gz    binary
*.parquet binary
*.pkl   binary
*.joblib binary
*.lgb   binary
*.db    binary
*.sqlite binary
